      • SECURITY_KEYBOARD_LOCATION

        public static final java.lang.String SECURITY_KEYBOARD_LOCATION
        Broadcast Action: specifies security location.
        "com.pax.us.pay.SECURITY_KEYBOARD_LOCATION"

        BroadPOS send the location information of keyboard to security UI, and security UI will handle it if need.

        Output: StatusData.PARAM_X - is X coordinate of keyboard
        Type: Integer
        Unit: pixel

        Output: StatusData.PARAM_Y - is Y coordinate of keyboard
        Type: Integer
        Unit: pixel

        Output: StatusData.PARAM_WIDTH - is width of keyboard
        Type: Integer
        Unit: pixel

        Output: StatusData.PARAM_HEIGHT - is height of keyboard
        Type: Integer
        Unit: pixel

        See Also:
